.Dt CITRUN-TERM 1
.Os
.Sh NAME
.Nm citrun-term
.Nd terminal viewer
.Sh DESCRIPTION
Listens for a connection from a single running instrumented program. Displays
execution data in a terminal window.
.Sh FILES
.Bl -tag -width Ds
.It Pa /tmp/citrun.socket
Listen socket.
.El
.Sh EXIT STATUS
.Ex -std
.Sh SEE ALSO
.Xr citrun-gl 1
